The paper deals with vehicle detection and annotation using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for this task also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with real-world traffic surveillance data, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or robotics (cs.RO) depending on the specific application.
